l2tabs.configuration.attributeLinePerPag: Number of attribute lines per page
l2tabs.configuration.attributeSettings.t:
COMMON: Show only common attributes and L2 attributes
ALL: Show all attributes in attribute type, similar to Apothic Attributes
ALL_EXCEPT_UNCHANGED: Show all, but hide attributes that are unchanged
Allowed Values: COMMON, ALL, ALL_EXCEPT_UNCHANGED
l2tabs.configuration.hiddenTabs.tooltip:
List of tabs to hide
Example: "attribute" for attribute tab
Example: "curios" for curios tab
Example: "pandora" for pandora tab
l2tabs.configuration.redirectInventoryTa: Redirect Inventory Tab to Curios Inventory
l2tabs.configuration.showTabsOnlyCurio.t:
Show inventory tabs only in curio page.
Only works when showTabs is true and curio is installed.
For users who have other tabs conflicting with this mod
